    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Mac comes with the JDK, for more information check: </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://developer.apple.com/mac/library/documentation/Java/Conceptual/Java14Development/02-JavaDevTools/JavaDevTools.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://developer.apple.com/mac/library/documentation/Java/Conceptual/Java14Development/02-JavaDevTools/JavaDevTools.html</a></p>\n"
