    "question_id" : 1577014,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h1>In 2025, give a try to <a href=\"https://sdkman.io/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>sdkman</code></a>, is better than <code>brew</code></h1>\n<pre><code>curl -s &quot;https://get.sdkman.io&quot; | bash\n</code></pre>\n<p>then open a <strong>new shell</strong> and try <code>list</code> to see what you could install ;-)</p>\n<pre><code>sdk list java \n</code></pre>\n<p>At time of writing you could use:</p>\n<pre><code>sdk install java 17.0.1-tem\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
